# Output Center Rule

## Source Of Truth
- If this file conflicts with [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md), **CLAUDE.md wins**.

## Output Center Is First-Class
Output Center is not a simple export button collection.

## Priority Documents (Current Phase)
- 購入提案書 (Proposal)
- 費用見積明細書 (Estimate Sheet)
- 資金計画書 (Funding Plan)
- 前提条件説明書 (Assumption Memo)

## Must-Have Quality Gate
Before generation:
- Required fields check
- Template/version check
- Document control metadata check

After generation:
- Record source data references
- Record template version
- Record actor and timestamp
- Keep output history searchable/exportable

